Shrimp Risotto $13 - Chef Hong uses every single part of the shrimp and coaxed so much flavor out of the juicy shrimp head. You could really taste the deep flavor of the sweet ocean in the risotto.

The pistachio rose creme brûlée was TO DIE FOR. Usually, desserts with rose flavors either completely lack the essence of it or don't do it justice. This creme brûlée was the perfect balance of pistachio and rose, with a flamed, crisp top to contrast the decadent overall creaminess. I wish I didn't share it three-ways. I'm getting one for myself next time.
